<div id='docs'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class="blog-header">
      <h1 class="blog-title">Big Earth Blockchain Docs</h1>
      <p class="lead blog-description">The official documentation of the Big Earth Blockchain Platform.</p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8 blog-main">
          <div class="blog-post">
            <p>Here you'll find everything you need to get started on the Big Earth Blockchain Platform.</p>
            <ul>
              <li><%= link_to 'Developers', docs_developers_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to 'API', docs_api_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to 'Security', docs_security_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to 'Credit', docs_credit_path %></li>
