            <p>Have an urgent matter that you need to get in touch w/ us about? Email us at one of the addresses below.</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>security@bigearth.io</strong> for any security related questions/comments.</li>
              <li><strong>support@bigearth.io</strong> for any general support related questions/comments.</li>
            </ul>
          </div><!-- /.blog-post -->
        </div><!-- /.blog-main -->
        <%= render 'nav' %>
      </div><!-- /.row -->  
    </div>
  </div>
